# - Config file for the genbb_help package
# It defines the following variables
#  genbb_help_INCLUDE_DIRS - include directories for genbb_help
#  genbb_help_LIBRARY      - libraries to link against
#  genbb_help_BIO_LIBRARY  - library targets to link against (Boost I/O library)
#  genbb_help_REFLECTION_LIBRARY - library targets to link against (reflection library)
#  genbb_help_LIBRARIES    - libraries to link against
#  genbb_help_WITH_BIO     - flag for Boost/Serialization I/O DLL (a.k.a. 'bio')
#  genbb_help_WITH_REFLECTION  - flag for reflection DLL
#  genbb_help_WITH_FORTRAN  - flag for Fortran

